            <div class="w-16 sm:w-20 h-1 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full mx-auto"></div>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 sm:mb-8">
            I specialize in working with adults (20s-60s) and seniors(60s+) who are navigating life's ever- changing challenges. I use an eclectic, psychodynamic, strengths-based approach that incorporates positive psychology, mindfulness, attachment theory, cognitive behavioral therapies, and self-care.
