          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
            <div class="bg-emerald-50 rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-6">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-2 text-sm sm:text-base">Adults 20 - 60s</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">Each stage of adulthood has unique and universal challenges that impact our day-to-day experience. Concerns will be addressed from a holistic perspective, integrating your general well-being with the demands of your life.</p>
